Date of Birth: February 22, 1811<br/>
Birthplace: Mendon, Massachusetts, USA<br/>
Ordained apostle: July 16, 1846<br/>
Death: September 3, 1869<br/>
<br/>
Born Feb. 22, 1811, at Mendon, Worcester Co., Massachusetts, to John Benson and Chloe Taft. Ordained apostle July 16, 1846, by Brigham Young at Council Bluffs, Iowa, at age 35; died Sept. 3, age 58.